This simple WCF3/WBB3 plugin provides a way to automatically add an user to a group if he's got an mail which is listed in a certain file.

Installation:
=============
. change emailValidator.php and insert the accepted emails
. upload emailValidator.php to some directory
. change groupID in RegisterMail2GroupListener.class.php to your group's ID
. change include path in RegisterMail2GroupListener.class.php relative to the WCF directory
. run build.sh to build the plugin tarball
. upload plugin to WCF3/WBB3


